column5: June 30th deadline.  Just called mine in over the phone.
Yep. Always have beter luck when I do it hand delivery

Got a question for ya Brian.  If the WMA you're applying for has an "A", "b", c.....  does your antlerless tag let you hunt in all of them.  Cuz the one I applied to goes up to "e", and they never asked my which one I wanted.
I apply for 76 the whole area. It only matters for the controlled hunt.
i did mine over the phone last night.  first yr hunting and i cant wait!
Thanks for the reminder!!! I'm reaching for the phone now....
